{"tid":682343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"脫毒其實唔難㗎","createTime":"2018-05-28T20:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T21:30:34.000Z","uid":152048,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8bdee843cea54e88887454a5af356c044a201eac","tid":682343,"uid":152048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T20:20:53.000Z","msg":"首先 儲少少錢 買啲衫唔好着到咁柒咁毒 人地都唔會對你有咩意見<br />\n<br />\n然後講嘢嗰陣畀啲自信! 每個同你唔熟嘅人同你講嘢其實都係唔知你以前(或者依家)都係on99嚟㗎<br />\n<br />\n大家畀啲自信自己啦! 我上年仲係一條毒撚 今年發生咗好多嘢識咗多咗人 改變咗過往嘅自己 其實大家都可以㗎<br />\n<br />\n當然溝女又係另一樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊黎脫毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dc8c3c73a151723880b6e0158f363e5ed1baa5","tid":682343,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T20:21:51.000Z","msg":"咪又係毒撚"},{"pid":"4ef90fb492e326ef53bc04e201e709d87baf6d9b","tid":682343,"uid":171598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T20:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/042136_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F042136_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e252d081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/042202_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F042202_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=8e464018&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ad96c550c6dbffa578774863784ad7a89cf8e00","tid":682343,"uid":152048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83dc8c3c73a151723880b6e0158f363e5ed1baa5","tid":682343,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T20:21:51.000Z","msg":"咪又係毒撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T20:22:28.000Z","msg":"毒撚同social撚一線之差㗎喳"},{"pid":"b196332c6